Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.22,0:00:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼模仿出寧次的查克拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吸取別人的查克拉加以利用 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就能變出同樣的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻大戰正如火如荼地進行著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時 我方部隊裏混入了白絕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.72,0:00:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部隊周邊設有結界 所以無法輕易入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過看來結界有了漏洞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們八班前來探查究竟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.46,0:00:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這不是深入虎穴了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:00:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下就清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.79,0:01:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是結界的漏洞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.17,0:01:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙就是從這裏混進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來數量不少 小心行事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.81,0:01:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白眼 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙通牙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘術.蟲玉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.62,0:01:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.86,0:01:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要貿然去碰那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.18,0:01:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問為何的話 他會吸收我們的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.34,0:01:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可如果不碰他們 怎麼攻擊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才放出了通信貓頭鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印班很快就能趕來封印這個礦洞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來只能撐到那一刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.18,0:02:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這樣下去情況越來越糟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.49,0:02:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田 牙 志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是封印班嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即將這裏封印
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.09,0:02:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請迅速離開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.52,0:02:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻煩 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通牙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 地面有油…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用於挖掘的起爆符
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 要爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤丸 空中動態追蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真淒慘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃 雛田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.49,0:05:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到這種地方會有起爆符
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之得趕緊去找雛田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙 你的鼻子聞不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 煙味過於濃烈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田 雛田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法感知到敵方的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來那些白色的傢伙被炸飛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不幸中的萬幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連出口都被炸掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙 志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地表突然破裂 我掉到下層了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印班應該還有一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕緊去解救他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊找到他 然後逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他並非被炸死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是被苦無給刺死的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這傢伙在爆炸前就被刺死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是 還有殘餘的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能變成所吸查克拉的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果是它的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會設法混入隊伍裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就說 我們之中有冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是一班的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人假冒一定能發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田 為何不用白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為封印班的結界術還沒完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以白眼受到了干擾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼質疑起雛田了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙 你的鼻子真派不上用場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼連我都懷疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話 你又是真身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的戰鬥 我並未碰到那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 蟲子身上也能吸取到你的查克拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話 我確實無法證明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然也是本人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無意義的爭論
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問為何的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都無法證明自己的真偽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果都不可信 就單獨行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己去找剩下的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們無法互相信任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了 能幫我一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現第二名犧牲者了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慘了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我們之中有冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少裝蒜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害人手中正抓著這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從氣味來看 是你衣服上的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃 你就是冒牌貨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:09:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪你突然說什麼冒牌貨…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就覺得你不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服碎片應該是剛才爆炸時造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何還特意說出那些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就說出來反而不容易被懷疑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我可不會輕易上當
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 牙 雛田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被冒牌貨挑撥的話 會自相殘殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙正等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能順它的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前可以確定一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒牌貨只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問為何的話 如果有兩個冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就會毫無顧慮地攻擊我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 那傢伙想坐收漁人之利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總不能一直耗著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一個好辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜拳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜拳 石頭 剪子 布嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了要回答大家的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按順序回答不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 要猜拳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥要在這裏猜拳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭 剪子 布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭 剪子 布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛肉幹 還有和赤丸散步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭 剪子 布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平了繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭 剪子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 這猜拳沒必要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這個很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭 剪子 布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.23,0:12:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡的東西是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡的東西是甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.90,0:12:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 有什麼不對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡的不是鳴人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在難道是這類提問的環節嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑 開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 嚴肅的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管了 繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭 剪子 布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平了繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你輸了 換我提問
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:13:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個只有真的志乃才能回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪回佐助那次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你沒被選入隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個問題無法回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是不想回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這些不就毫無意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道真相的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就打倒我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是有意義的 猜拳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭 剪子 布
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭 剪子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不用猜拳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭 剪子 布
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪到志乃了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場勝負到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼擅自決定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然大和隊長被捕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:14:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們很可能已經弄到了我們的個人情報
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們怎麼會關心我們的個人情報
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問為何的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們打算偽裝成我們中的一員戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣 每人的興趣和怪癖都是重要的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說倒也在理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼之前做的事情豈不是毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓我說多少遍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜拳是有目的的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然無法信任你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你們兩個一起幹掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃 你這是幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 下手這麼重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙通牙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙 我也助你一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定是個冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼大的火 他無法使用蟲子了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧 看招 牙通牙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來就能出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 就剩我一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真身登場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是冒牌貨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被問到奇怪的問題時 我還擔心暴露了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如那傢伙所說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸虧從大和那裏掌握了關於你們的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利讓你們的關係破裂真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有狗幫你 我贏定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 我將真的志乃給…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太愚蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問為何的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你真的很笨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於原形畢露了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著 怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你 我不得不犧牲重要的蟲子們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲子 剛才打倒的是蟲分身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道我是冒牌貨的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒認出誰是冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初 我們三人對峙時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中便一直在思量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便三人之中有冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一直偽裝下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下得了手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔拳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經交心的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的能對外表是同伴的傢伙下手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後 還有更為白癡的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被那種傢伙打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概也心甘情願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到一個簡單的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 不如讓真正的我去送死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來 你一定會現身的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我才把一切都賭在猜拳上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜拳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你的暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 這猜拳沒必要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這個很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一說 我就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時你想傳達的是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“按照我的指示來行動”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後你又說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道真相的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就打倒我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不太清楚是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既然攻擊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就條件反射地將你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧你打倒了我的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙現出了原形
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且讀懂了我的暗號 說明你是真的牙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞這麼多花樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我把你們兩一起收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問為何的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:19:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經完全陷入我的忍術之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為死於你之手的兩人報的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘術.蟲龍卷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之要謝謝你 志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我依然很猶豫是否跟同伴對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒全力用牙通牙對付我的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不正是你想要的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你也向我進攻了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時真假不明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是裝模作樣的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不能打女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡裝紳士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然打倒了冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.15,0:19:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但雛田本人在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧 雛田
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我排最後嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.99,0:20:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼特別的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這次事件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.77,0:20:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點就將忍者聯軍的最高機密洩露給那些傢伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高機密是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡鳴人這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為牙想開你的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心說漏嘴了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 那些傢伙為了變化成我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎從大和隊長那兒得到很多個人情報
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.91,0:20:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…這麼一來…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.49,0:20:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道只有大和隊長才知道的那個秘密也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的秘密也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個秘密也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要將他們趕盡殺絕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個不留
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.91,0:22:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,佐助 你怎麼還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.27,0:22:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,鳴人在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,誰知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,現在你的敵人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:22:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,我找鳴人有事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:22:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.91,0:23:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,從來沒把我放在眼裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,真沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.70,0:23:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,藝術家的美學
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.66,0:23:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,我要把你這目中無人的臉打變形了
